Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.69,0:01:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 快起來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.52,0:01:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,東北戰區裡撿到的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.12,0:01:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,名字還沒起
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.71,0:01:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我就叫她「你」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.46,0:01:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 快打招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.12,0:01:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,別這麼粗暴 她還是個孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.02,0:01:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,吉爾 它不是孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.79,0:02:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,它是武器
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.00,0:02:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,武器？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.27,0:02:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,戰鬥用的道具 而已
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.56,0:02:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.25,0:02:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我來收養她
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.27,0:02:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.65,0:02:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,你願意接受真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.40,0:02:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我已經跟陸軍那邊打過招呼了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.87,0:02:25.37,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\pos(548,500)}萊登莎伏特里希
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.87,0:02:25.37,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\be3\pos(440,744)\fad(0,0)}海軍司令部
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.64,0:02:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我想見迪特弗里德·布甘比利亞大佐！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.77,0:02:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,都說了 你不能見大佐！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.32,0:02:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我有急事要跟他確認！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.54,0:02:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,真煩人！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.45,0:02:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你們在搞什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.78,0:02:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,大佐 非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.66,0:02:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,那個女的一直吵著要找大佐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.37,0:02:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你退下去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.25,0:02:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,還想要命的話
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.46,0:02:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你來這裡幹什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.17,0:02:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,大佐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.63,0:03:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,到底武器還是武器
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.59,0:03:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,大佐！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.78,0:03:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,少佐他 吉爾伯特少佐他…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.48,0:03:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,失蹤了…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.84,0:03:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,是真的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.59,0:03:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,原來你不知道嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.25,0:03:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,吉爾伯特…已經…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.20,0:03:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,胡說！胡說！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.87,0:03:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,少佐一定沒有事的！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.24,0:03:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你這表情是什麼意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.66,0:03:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,對他來說 只是個道具的你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.81,0:03:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有感情 只是個道具的你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.30,0:03:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼會感到悲傷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.07,0:03:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎麼跟她說了啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.07,0:03:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我覺得她現在已經能夠接受事實了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.99,0:03:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,白痴！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.26,0:03:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎麼總是這麼盲目樂觀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.85,0:03:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,而且一如既往的不懂女人心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.81,0:03:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,快給我去把那個孩子找回來！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.54,0:03:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 我明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.18,0:04:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀 少爺
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.01,0:04:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,還有…這個孩子是？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.81,0:04:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,總之先帶她去洗個澡 然後給她換身衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.69,0:04:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,請問… 跟夫人怎麼說？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.19,0:04:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,夫人現在在萊登的公館
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.79,0:04:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,不需要告訴她
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.85,0:04:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我需要收留她一段時間
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.45,0:04:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,這邊請
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.36,0:04:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.69,0:04:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,好痛！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.33,0:04:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 不要啊！ 痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.01,0:04:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.71,0:04:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,少爺 雖然我幫她換好衣服了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.13,0:04:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,但這孩子實在太調皮了…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.42,0:05:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,不 這樣就好 沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.39,0:05:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,先給她吃飯 然後帶到客房去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.78,0:05:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,麻煩你了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.48,0:05:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣會…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.40,0:05:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣會感冒的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.33,0:05:23.47,Default,,0,0,0,,蓋上毯子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.61,0:05:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,明天還會更冷的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.54,0:05:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,給我站住
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.75,0:05:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,不行 不能到外面去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.11,0:05:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.61,0:05:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.09,0:05:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,這孩子 一直在找少爺
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.96,0:05:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,連飯也不吃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.94,0:05:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,還不能帶她去前線
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.02,0:05:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,那個少女狀態太不穩定了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.80,0:06:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你為什麼反對
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.65,0:06:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,這可是上面的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.20,0:06:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你也看到那傢伙在訓練場上的表現了才對
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.20,0:06:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,除了殺人 一點用處都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.91,0:06:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,給我帶去看看
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.00,0:06:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.02,0:06:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,別這麼生氣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.99,0:06:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,像這種沒爹沒娘的小丫頭
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.83,0:06:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,派得上用場就只管用
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.23,0:06:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,要是她沒用了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.77,0:06:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,丟在戰場上就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.01,0:06:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,那孩子還…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.05,0:06:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,閉嘴！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.05,0:06:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,夠了 跟你這種偽君子無話可說
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.35,0:06:32.07,Default,,0,0,0,,這是命令 就說這麼多
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.62,0:06:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,蓋爾達里克帝國同盟軍已經入侵波奇亞查
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.33,0:06:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然我們立刻在波奇亞查首都
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.29,0:06:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,卡普里亞外圍的河流建立了防線
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.12,0:06:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,但現在陷入持久戰
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.71,0:07:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我方軍力只有3萬
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.67,0:07:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,對方有6萬
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.59,0:07:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然我們現在維持住了防線
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.99,0:07:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,但敵軍把大炮調到了前線
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.93,0:07:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,在那之後 由於遭到炮擊 我方士氣低落
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.82,0:07:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,陣線有可能崩潰
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.63,0:07:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡 布甘比利亞少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.63,0:07:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.39,0:07:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我想讓你帶一個中隊 去破壞大炮
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.12,0:07:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.14,0:07:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,保證完成任務
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.86,0:07:26.39,Default,,0,0,0,,你就留在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.95,0:07:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,在我回來之前哪都不要去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.80,0:07:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,明白嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.25,0:07:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,少佐 我們準備好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.85,0:07:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我這就去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.51,0:07:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,少佐 有哨兵
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.75,0:08:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.16,0:08:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,發生什麼事了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.71,0:08:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,敵襲！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.29,0:08:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,敵襲！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.02,0:08:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,快聯絡指揮部！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.63,0:08:25.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我部遭萊登莎伏特里希襲擊！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.92,0:08:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,快迎戰！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.92,0:08:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,隊長 敵軍接近了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.90,0:08:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,突擊！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.86,0:09:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.98,0:09:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.62,0:09:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,少佐他…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.81,0:09:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,少佐他在嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.91,0:09:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,少佐他 在這裡的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.44,0:09:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,少爺他…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.11,0:10:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,「吉爾伯特·布甘比利亞」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.72,0:10:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,,少佐的名字…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.74,0:10:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,980)\fs54}Violet
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.74,0:10:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,紫羅蘭
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.92,0:10:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1060,980)\fs54}Violet
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.92,0:10:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你就叫薇鷗萊特
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.07,0:10:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你的未來不是道具
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.19,0:10:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,而是與這個名字相稱的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.20,0:10:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,薇… 薇鷗…萊特
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.14,0:10:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,原來你會說話的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.65,0:10:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,少…佐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.76,0:10:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,薇鷗萊… 萊特
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.71,0:10:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.08,0:10:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,你是薇鷗萊特
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.97,0:10:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,而我是少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.57,0:10:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.93,0:10:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,少佐 我讀完了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.07,0:10:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,好 下次教你寫字
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.17,0:11:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,少佐 這是報告書
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.51,0:11:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.67,0:11:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,寫得不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.59,0:11:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,正好也能兼作練字
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.32,0:11:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,以後每天都要交報告
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.21,0:11:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,明白了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.64,0:11:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,毎日都要交報告
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.14,0:11:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\move(1040,1060,940,1060,0,3000)\blur6}雖然我們沒有找到他本人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.85,0:11:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\move(940,1030,1040,1030,0,3000)\blur6}少爺他…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.36,0:11:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\move(1040,1060,940,1060,0,3000)\blur6}但在瓦礫之下找到了他的名牌
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.82,0:11:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\move(940,1030,1040,1030,0,3000)\blur6}九泉之下的吉爾伯特也…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.60,0:11:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\move(1040,1060,940,1060,0,3000)\blur6}所以把他算作了失蹤…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.56,0:11:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,977)\t(1593,2010,1,\blur12)}吉爾伯特…已經…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.32,0:11:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,今天是感恩節
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.12,0:11:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,三年來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.63,0:11:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡一直被蓋爾達里克軍占領
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.37,0:11:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,如今終於得到了解放
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.33,0:11:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,薇鷗萊特
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.93,0:11:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,這都是你的功勞
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.54,0:11:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,梅希蒂希這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.83,0:11:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,有著在感恩節這天給想要感謝的人送禮的習俗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.72,0:12:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,薇鷗萊特
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.60,0:12:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,你有什麼想要的東西嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.73,0:12:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,想要的…東西？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.75,0:12:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.11,0:12:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,想要什麼都可以跟我說
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.22,0:12:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.29,0:12:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,只要是少佐的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.08,0:12:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,這不是命令
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.57,0:12:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,是我想感謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.20,0:12:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,感謝？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.86,0:12:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.95,0:12:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你總是奮勇作戰…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.61,0:12:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.67,0:12:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我們走走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.87,0:12:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.88,0:12:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我想要的 東西 應該是什麼樣的呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.19,0:12:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.29,0:12:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,像你這麼大的女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.31,0:12:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,應該想要裙子和首飾
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.09,0:12:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.16,0:12:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我想要裙子和首飾
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.17,0:13:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.30,0:13:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡有少佐的眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.68,0:13:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,和少佐的眼睛 是一樣的顏色
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.57,0:13:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,當我看到它的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.67,0:13:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,這種…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.28,0:13:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,該怎麼說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.78,0:13:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,意下如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.04,0:13:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,這胸針很美麗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.63,0:13:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,美…麗…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.08,0:13:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.13,0:13:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道什麼是「美麗」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.00,0:14:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,是和「漂亮」相近的詞彙嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.80,0:14:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,是的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.31,0:14:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,不選你眼睛的顏色嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.35,0:14:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,因為 這就是最「美麗」的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.53,0:14:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,之前我不知道這個詞 所以從來沒有跟您說過
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.78,0:14:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,但自從見到少佐眼睛的那一刻 我就覺得很美麗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.36,0:14:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.87,0:14:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,把胸針給我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.16,0:14:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.03,0:14:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.81,0:15:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.84,0:15:12.80,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fad(450,0)\blur3\pos(553,386)}西部戰線
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.84,0:15:12.80,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fad(450,0)\blur3\pos(460,660)}歐巴伯格
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.80,0:15:16.35,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\pos(1860,530)}萊登莎伏特里希軍
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.80,0:15:16.35,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\pos(1770,784)}前線指揮部
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.38,0:15:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,聽說蓋爾達里克連西部基地都放棄了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.59,0:15:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,看來不到開春就能回老家了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.60,0:15:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,要大家一起回去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.63,0:15:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.13,0:15:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,吉爾伯特
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.93,0:15:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,好久不見
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.64,0:15:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,霍金斯中佐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.96,0:15:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,別叫我中佐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.76,0:15:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,這可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.52,0:15:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你的軍階比我高
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.86,0:15:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,好久沒看到你這冷淡的態度
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.76,0:15:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,倒開始覺得有點可愛了 真是神奇
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.32,0:15:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你也是一點都沒變
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.20,0:15:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,只有軍銜變成中佐了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.87,0:15:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我是因為總被安排到那些不戰而勝的戰事裡去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.38,0:16:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你家裡可是我軍的大金主
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.37,0:16:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,指揮部當然也會照顧你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.70,0:16:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,所以啊 升階了反而覺得丟臉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.93,0:16:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,別說這個了 你還好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.80,0:16:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,好好吃飯了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.25,0:16:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,睡好了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.69,0:16:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,他只是在開玩笑 不要緊張
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.11,0:16:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然年紀比我大 但他是我士官學校時的同學
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.57,0:16:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,上次在訓練場見過的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.60,0:16:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你還把她帶在身邊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.86,0:16:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,就是她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.90,0:16:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,在卡普里亞一戰立下腥風血雨的戰功的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.88,0:16:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,大家背地裡都管她叫少佐的「武器」了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.15,0:16:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,就不能讓她做點別的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.63,0:16:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,不 不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.30,0:16:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.58,0:16:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,她叫薇鷗萊特
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.76,0:16:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我給她取的 因為她沒有名字
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.68,0:16:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,收復英騰斯的這一仗你也要派她？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.36,0:17:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,只要這一仗打勝了 敵軍就全線崩潰了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.23,0:17:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,恐怕 這就是我們最後一戰了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.28,0:17:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.45,0:17:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.62,0:17:16.97,Default,,0,0,0,,戰爭結束以後打算退伍開個公司
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.54,0:17:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,開公司？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.80,0:17:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,到時候我會聘你的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.00,0:17:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我可不想在你手下做事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.17,0:17:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,那我就雇薇鷗萊特吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.65,0:17:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.11,0:17:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,或許是個好主意
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.58,0:17:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,集合！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.84,0:17:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.41,0:17:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.21,0:17:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,您已經不需要我了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.92,0:17:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.87,0:18:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,處理我的結果
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.79,0:18:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,是轉屬到霍金斯中佐手下去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.26,0:18:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,少佐不會再給我命令了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.85,0:18:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,不是你的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.94,0:18:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,還有幾個小時就要決戰了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.44,0:18:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,這件事情下次再說
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.78,0:18:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我來說明作戰方案
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.07,0:18:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,敵軍的總司令部就在英騰斯這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.33,0:18:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,其四周都是懸崖峭壁 可謂是天然的要塞
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.41,0:18:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,從正面恐怕難以突破
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.11,0:18:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我們先由主力部隊進行炮擊轉移敵軍注意力
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.62,0:18:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,利用這個機會我們從下水道攻入英騰斯內部
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.34,0:18:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,衝進大教堂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.59,0:18:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,控制敵軍指揮部
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.26,0:18:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,然後我們會發射信號彈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.57,0:18:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,向我軍發出全軍衝鋒的信號
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.85,0:18:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,這就是我們的作戰方案
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.44,0:18:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,聽好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.31,0:18:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.94,0:19:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,還有5分鐘炮擊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.82,0:19:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,好 給我上！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.96,0:19:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,炮擊開始
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.05,0:19:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,炮擊開始！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.93,0:19:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,發射！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.30,0:19:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,跟上去！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.78,0:19:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,各班 報告狀況
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.24,0:19:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,1班有3個人犧牲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.40,0:19:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,2班幾乎毫髮無傷
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.87,0:19:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,3班和4班有一半都掉隊了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.37,0:20:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,狀態不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.12,0:20:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,好 1班2班死守四周
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.22,0:20:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,不要讓敵軍增援靠近
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.41,0:20:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,3班4班跟上來的人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.60,0:20:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,跟我一起去控制大教堂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.23,0:20:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,上！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.99,0:20:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.55,0:20:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,發射！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.94,0:20:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,吉爾伯特 好好做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.52,0:20:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,發射！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.96,0:20:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,少佐！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.90,0:21:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,向右轉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.43,0:21:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,全軍 突擊！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.78,0:21:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,少佐…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.24,0:22:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,少佐…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.34,0:22:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,少佐！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.29,0:22:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,少佐！少佐！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.67,0:22:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我…沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.61,0:22:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,少佐！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.11,0:22:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,別管我 快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.26,0:22:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,快逃啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.50,0:22:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我做不到！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.53,0:22:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我要帶著少佐一起逃
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.16,0:22:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我就在…這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.92,0:23:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,那我不逃了！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.96,0:23:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,如果少佐說要留下來 我就在這裡戰鬥到底
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.08,0:23:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,如果少佐說要逃的話 我就帶著少佐一起逃
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.60,0:23:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,薇鷗萊特！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.81,0:24:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,絕對！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.94,0:24:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,絕對不會讓少佐你死的！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.41,0:24:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.00,0:24:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,夠了！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.01,0:24:31.99,Default,,0,0,0,,活下去…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.80,0:24:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,薇鷗萊特
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.35,0:24:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你要…活下去…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.69,0:24:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,自由地活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.65,0:24:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我真心地…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.98,0:24:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,愛著你
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.77,0:25:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,愛？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.11,0:25:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,請問「愛」是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.25,0:25:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,請問「愛」…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.80,0:25:14.87,Default,,0,0,0,,是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.72,0:25:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我…不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.13,0:25:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我完全不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.19,0:25:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,少佐！
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.03,0:26:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我就覺得你會來這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.57,0:26:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,這場戰鬥…真的很慘烈呢
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.60,0:26:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你們發射信號彈之後 我們全軍突擊
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.94,0:26:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,自知大勢已去的蓋爾達里克軍
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.66,0:26:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,在撤退之前 炮轟了自己的總司令部
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.48,0:26:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你是在這個台階下面被發現的
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.71,0:26:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,恐怕 是那傢伙為了保護你
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.04,0:26:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,在炮擊的瞬間把你推下來的
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.86,0:26:48.07,Default,,0,0,0,,在住院的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.02,0:26:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,不論問誰 都跟我說少佐沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.12,0:26:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,大家都說不出口啊
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.61,0:27:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,因為你比起自己 要更擔心那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.48,0:27:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.85,0:27:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,薇鷗萊特
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.80,0:27:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,要去…
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.72,0:27:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,哪裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.99,0:27:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,除了少佐身在的地方…我哪裡都去不了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.44,0:27:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我們回公司去
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.85,0:27:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你是我們公司的 自動筆記人偶啊
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.69,0:27:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,那我也待在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.89,0:27:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,直到你願意一起回去為止
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.35,0:27:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,因為那傢伙…把你託付給了我
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.96,0:27:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,就在決戰開始前
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.21,0:27:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,那傢伙特地來找我說——
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.18,0:27:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur6}萬一我有個三長兩短
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.50,0:27:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur6}薇鷗萊特就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.84,0:28:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur6}等戰爭結束後
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.23,0:28:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur6}請把她送到萊登的艾媧嘉登家
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.18,0:28:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur6}吉爾伯特
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.82,0:28:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur6}拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.53,0:28:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.14,0:28:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,從來沒有 把你當作是戰鬥用的道具
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.74,0:28:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,而是把你當作一個女孩子 為你的將來著想
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.36,0:28:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.92,0:28:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思了 強行把你拖上來
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.76,0:28:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.74,0:28:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,應該沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.13,0:29:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,剛出院的那陣子 我還在想到底該怎麼辦才好
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.57,0:29:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,但是你現在 已經能夠好好完成人偶的工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.10,0:29:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你真的很努力
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.50,0:29:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,哪怕沒有…
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.86,0:29:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,那傢伙的命令 相信你也能夠活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.21,0:29:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur6}少佐不會再給我命令了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.21,0:29:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur6}不是你的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.97,0:29:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur6}這件事情下次再說
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.77,0:29:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,公路被封鎖了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.57,0:29:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,中佐
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.58,0:29:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我已經退…
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.81,0:29:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,也罷 稍息
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.58,0:29:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.25,0:29:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,發生什麼事了？
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.71,0:29:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,克斯科萊爾城遭到了蓋爾達里克的反動分子襲擊
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.81,0:29:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,確實聽說過反動勢力日漸抬頭…
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.63,0:30:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,現在狀況如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.95,0:30:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然已經控制了局面
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.64,0:30:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,但還不能解除周邊的警戒
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.58,0:30:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,換條路走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.93,0:30:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.29,0:30:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,薇鷗萊特回來了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.67,0:30:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,好像是
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.01,0:30:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,她還會回來上班的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.53,0:30:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,你去看看她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.35,0:30:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你去不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.14,0:30:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你這樣的人去正好合適
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.27,0:30:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,「我這樣的」是什麼樣的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.28,0:30:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我這邊可忙著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.58,0:30:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,本尼迪克特
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.56,0:30:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,你能去12區那邊找找嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.69,0:31:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我去14區看看
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.57,0:31:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,發生什麼事了？
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.03,0:31:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,新來的快遞員把送不完的信給丟掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.03,0:31:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.11,0:31:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我們要去找回來
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.23,0:31:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,別擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.49,0:31:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我們大致猜得到丟在哪裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.73,0:31:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,薇鷗萊特 你在吧
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.65,0:31:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我不久留 讓我進來坐坐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.69,0:31:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,讓您操心了…
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.37,0:31:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,非常抱歉…
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.91,0:31:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你身體還好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.70,0:31:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,好好吃飯了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.83,0:31:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我給你送的東西 就放這了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.37,0:32:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你明天能出來嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.01,0:32:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,大家都在等你
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.18,0:32:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,點名要你的委託也有好多
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.59,0:32:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我就像…
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.99,0:32:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.59,0:32:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,霍金斯社長所說的那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.02,0:32:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,燒起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.10,0:32:23.47,Default,,0,0,0,,因為自己曾經做過的事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.77,0:32:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur6}總有一天 你會明白我所說的
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.30,0:32:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur6}然後你會發覺
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.90,0:32:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur6}自己滿身火燒火燎的傷痕
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.31,0:32:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼要跟她說這種話啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.50,0:32:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你想想她的遭遇 這不是毫無辦法的事情嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.97,0:32:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,不管有過什麼樣的遭遇
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.81,0:32:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,不管有著什麼樣的原委
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.54,0:32:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,自己做過的事情是不可抹消的
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.09,0:32:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,那就忘了過去 重新開始…
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.90,0:32:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,忘記也是不可能的 不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.51,0:32:58.99,Default,,0,0,0,,燒起來的 不僅僅是那孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.07,0:33:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,包括你我
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.65,0:33:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然表面上傷口似乎已經痊癒
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.39,0:33:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,但傷痕始終留在心間
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.43,0:33:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,那你說…
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.70,0:33:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,該如何是好呢？那孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.89,0:33:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,該怎麼做 只有她自己才能決定
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.18,0:33:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,在她正視並接受自己滿身瘡痍的身體之後
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.08,0:33:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.21,0:33:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,那孩子失去了少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.21,0:33:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,失去了她所有的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.79,0:33:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.03,0:33:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,因為她並沒有失去
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.93,0:33:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,一切都還在
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.53,0:33:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,嘉德麗雅也沒回來…
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.23,0:33:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,明天我去看看她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.33,0:33:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我覺得暫時應該讓她一個人靜一下…
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.45,0:33:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.49,0:33:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur6}我想理解…「我愛你」
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.91,0:34:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur6}我是為了理解少佐所說的「我愛你」
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.45,0:34:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur6}才來當人偶的
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.96,0:34:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,真的…
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.65,0:34:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,放著她一個人就好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.80,0:34:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.22,0:34:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣下去那孩子 會連人偶都不做了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.09,0:34:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我想找人代筆
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.81,0:34:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur6}少佐…
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.79,0:35:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur6}怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.23,0:35:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur6}薇鷗萊特
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.88,0:35:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur6}少佐 少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.64,0:35:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur6}您沒事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.73,0:35:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur6}你這身衣服是？
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.37,0:35:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur6}現在我在當自動筆記人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.32,0:35:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur6}你在？
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.48,0:35:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur6}是的 我的工作是代人寫信
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.59,0:35:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur6}寫信？
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.76,0:35:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur6}你那雙…荼毒生靈的手
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.86,0:35:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur6}少佐？
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.32,0:35:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur6}怎麼能寫出連結人心的信來？
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.41,0:36:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.79,0:37:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,少佐…
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.41,0:37:37.27,Default,,0,0,0,,少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.68,0:37:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我該怎麼辦…
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.80,0:37:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,請給我…
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.42,0:37:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,請給我…命令
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.66,0:38:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,有你的信
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.74,0:38:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,薇鷗萊特·艾媧嘉登
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.96,0:38:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,寫給你的
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.01,0:38:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,埃麗卡和艾麗絲託我送來的
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.06,0:38:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼 信你簽收了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.73,0:38:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,這麼晚了 還在送信嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.61,0:38:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.90,0:38:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,因為我們找到被丟掉的信了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.99,0:38:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,本尼迪克特呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.08,0:38:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,那傢伙 拐到腳了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.74,0:38:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,都怪他那雙鞋子
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.25,0:38:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的 你在搞什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.92,0:39:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,痛痛痛…好痛！
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.27,0:39:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,那我就去克拉夫特大街那邊了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.57,0:39:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,這條巷子就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.37,0:39:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,畢竟每一封信
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.07,0:39:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,都飽蘸著深情
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.05,0:39:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,每一封信都是必須要送到的
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.83,0:39:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,收到信了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.46,0:39:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,媽媽！
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.67,0:39:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,是爸爸寄來的
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.59,0:39:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,信送完了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.81,0:39:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.69,0:39:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.85,0:39:58.99,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了 每一封信都送到了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.21,0:40:18.77,Typing,,0,0,0,,薇鷗萊特 你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.95,0:40:21.56,Typing,,0,0,0,,我們本來想去看你的
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.49,0:40:25.41,Typing,,0,0,0,,但和艾麗絲商量了以後 我們決定給你寫信
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.70,0:40:30.16,Typing,,0,0,0,,人偶給人偶寫信或許很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.17,0:40:33.04,Typing,,0,0,0,,但是我想告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.73,0:40:35.12,Typing,,0,0,0,,我們在擔心你
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.76,0:40:37.71,Typing,,0,0,0,,還有 我們都在…
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.39,0:40:42.06,Typing,,0,0,0,,等你回來
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.44,0:40:48.17,Typing,,0,0,0,,現在 你大概沒有心情回來工作
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.57,0:40:49.66,Typing,,0,0,0,,先好好休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.36,0:40:54.27,Typing,,0,0,0,,萬一有什麼事情 請不要客氣 儘管找我們
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.95,0:40:58.63,Typing,,0,0,0,,我和艾麗絲都相信你一定會回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.81,0:41:09.57,Typing,,0,0,0,,還有 今天有個叫斯賓賽的人來找你代筆
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.10,0:41:14.57,Typing,,0,0,0,,說是想給妹妹寫一封致謝和道歉的信
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.29,0:41:18.07,Typing,,0,0,0,,他說一定要你來寫
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.65,0:41:22.44,Typing,,0,0,0,,不論如何 非你不可
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.95,0:41:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,請問這樣可以嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.04,0:41:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.37,0:41:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,給妹妹寫信 總覺得有點害臊
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.37,0:41:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,不過多虧了她 我找到了工作
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.05,0:41:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,而且有了重新開啟人生的信心
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.93,0:42:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,麻煩你了 特地來一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.07,0:42:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,聽說你最近在休息
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.02,0:42:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,是同事告訴我的
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.57,0:42:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,她們給我寫了信
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.27,0:42:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,那是 我今生收到的第一封信
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.35,0:42:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我理解了…
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.89,0:42:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,能收到別人給自己寫的信 是如此的開心
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.32,0:42:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,璐琪莉亞也一定會很高興的
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.99,0:42:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.36,0:43:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,「和這個名字…交相輝映」
Dialogue: 0,0:43:51.50,0:43:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,「與這個名字…相稱」
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.53,0:44:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,薇鷗萊特？
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.87,0:44:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,薇鷗萊特？
Dialogue: 0,0:44:30.32,0:44:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,正如社長所說的
Dialogue: 0,0:44:32.13,0:44:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我滿身火燒火燎的傷痕
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.80,0:44:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,可以嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:44:41.39,0:44:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以…做自動筆記人偶嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:44:48.43,0:44:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,活下去…
Dialogue: 0,0:44:50.17,0:44:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以…活下去嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:45:03.26,0:45:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,自己做過的事情是不可抹消的
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.80,0:45:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:45:45.45,0:45:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:45:49.41,0:45:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你作為自動筆記人偶做過的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:45:54.80,0:45:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,也是不可磨滅的
